  "title": "Warehouse Operator [WCNH]",
  "description": "<p><p>Accurately and efficiently <strong>prepare and pack orders</strong> for dispatch.</p></p><p><p>Handle <strong>loading and unloading of goods</strong> for storage and outbound deliveries.</p></p><p><p>Ensure compliance with <strong>warehouse safety regulations</strong> and maintain a clean, orderly workspace in line with <strong>5S standards</strong>.</p></p><p><p>Assist in <strong>inventory control activities</strong>, including cycle counts and periodic stocktakes.</p></p><p><p>Follow established <strong>warehouse operating procedures</strong> to ensure smooth daily operations.</p></p><p><p>Carry out other <strong>warehouse-related or ad-hoc duties</strong> as assigned by the Supervisor or Assistant Manager.<br /></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p></p>",
